    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "何を暗い顔して、ため息ついてんのよ\nポンコツマネージャー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why the gloomy face and sighs?\nWhat a clumsy manager you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6666667224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーがそんなだと\nアイドルにも伝染して、気分落ちるんですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the manager's like that‚\nthe mood of the idols will drop too‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.623180097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "仕事でポカしたとか？\n社長の逆鱗に触れて、明日にもクビになりそうとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you mess up at work or something?\nDid you incur the president's wrath and are on the verge of being fired tomorrow?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.400000469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "クビはまだ大丈夫なはずですけど\n実は、mihoさんとちょっと意見の相違が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should be fine with the firing part…\nActually‚ I had a little disagreement with miho-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.200000469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリ歴代優勝者達の祭典？\nそんなんやるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The festival of the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix's past winners?\nThey're actually doing that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6776185912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、サニピと月ストには麻奈の曲を歌ってもらって\nmihoさんにはSundanceの曲をと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we're having Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest sing Mana's songs‚\nand for miho-san‚ we're thinking of Sundance's songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7999997061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん、あいつが出る訳ないじゃん\n長瀬麻奈もSundanceもmihoの地雷っしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way she'd participate in that‚ right?\nBoth Nagase Mana and Sundance are landmines to miho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.855785657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_03_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "興味ないkanaにだって分かるのに\nなんでmihoに話す前に気付かないかなぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even kana‚ who's not interested‚ can see that‚\nwhy didn't you notice it before talking to miho?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1794324162,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}